    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">Minor change: Added -bar to all commands that do not take any arguments, so that these can be chained together. </td>
</tr>
<tr>
        <td class="roweven" valign="top" nowrap><a href="download_script.php?src_id=8330">IndentConsistencyCopAutoCmds.vim</a></td>
