    <td class="roweven" valign="top" width="2000">Avoiding multiple invocations of the IndentConsistencyCop when reloading or switching buffers. Now there's only one check per file and VIM session. <br>Added commands :IndentConsistencyCopAutoCmdsOn and :IndentConsistencyCopAutoCmdsOff to re-enable/disable autocommands.&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
</tr>
